-- | Description  : OD HoldsManagementFrameworke Index Creation                                 |  
-- | Purpose      : Create Custom Indexes.                                                      |
-- |                1. XX_OM_ODHOLDFRAMEWORK_U1 Unique Index on                                |
-- |                                             XX_OM_ODHOLDFRAMEWORK_TBL.HOLD_DEFINITION_ID  |
-- |                2. XX_OM_ODHOLDFRAMEWORK_N1 Composite Index on                             |
-- |                                             XX_OM_ODHOLDFRAMEWORK_TBL.HOLD_DEFINITION_ID  |
-- |                                           & XX_OM_ODHOLDFRAMEWORK_TBL.HOLD_ID             |
-- |Change Record:                                                                              |
-- |===============                                                                             |
-- |Version    Date          Author           Remarks                                           | 
-- |=======    ==========    =============    ==================================================+
-- |DRAFT 1A   03-May-2007   Nabarun Ghosh    Initial Version                                   |
-- |                                                                                            |
